# build
dist/

# Prisma migrations are SOURCE, not build output — they must be committed.
# `prisma migrate deploy` replays this folder to build the schema on every
# environment, so a clone without it creates no tables at all. (This entry was
# harmless while the project used `db push`; it is not any more.)

